\f2 M M IS: Inconsistent synchronization of microwave.Controller.powerLevel; locked 50% of time\'a0 Unsynchronized access at Controller.java:[line 160]
\f1 \

\f2 Analysis: The getPowerLevel() method isn't synchronized, even though other methods that change the power level are. This means a thread could call "get" and receive a value that is currently in the middle of being changed by another thread.
\f1 \
