\f2 M M IS: Inconsistent synchronization of microwave.Controller.prog; locked 66% of time\'a0 Unsynchronized access at Controller.java:[line 40]
\f1 \

\f2 Analysis: The prog variable is being accessed without a lock inside the reset() method, but it is locked in other places. This inconsistency means the microwave's programming state might not reset cleanly if another thread is trying to press a button at the same time.
